title: Creative Freelance Mastery: High income strategy, from your backyard!
description: How to run a high-yield freelance business, from your backyard. A super condensed proven strategy stepping through how to build your own business. Covering mindset, risk mitigation, diversity, our inner struggles, self-development and the differences between a high and low yield business. This book deals with what it takes to make the shift and how to break from convention towards a lifestyle on your terms.
author: Jonathan Northcott
